WEBVTT

1
02:48:17.010 --> 02:48:19.140 
用不着这么多
With a lesser sum, I have.

2
02:48:25.480 --> 02:48:27.310 
原谅我的冒昧
Forgive the intrusion.

3
02:48:27.400 --> 02:48:30.070 
你知道 我并不习惯不请自来
You know I'm not in the habit of coming into your house uninvited.

4
02:48:30.150 --> 02:48:32.240 
我这里一向都欢迎你
You've always been welcome here...

5
02:48:32.320 --> 02:48:34.400 
以学生的身份
as a pupil.

6
02:48:38.330 --> 02:48:40.990 
-你不是一个人来 -不
-You're not alone. -No.

7
02:48:42.790 --> 02:48:45.710 
你来有什么指教
This time you've come to teach.

8
02:48:47.330 --> 02:48:49.420 
你是柯萨斯的人
You've joined Crassus?

